App Name  : Tweet App

App Description : 
	Tweet app is used for post tweet with tags and repling back to posted tweet , user must login to add or view tweet .
	
Feature of TweetApp:
	1)Adding a post
	2)updating a post
	3)Like the post
	4)Repling to post
	5)User - login
	6)User - signUp
	
Technology :
	UI - Angular 11
	BackEnd - SpringBoot with maven
	DataBase - MongoDB
	Containerization -Docker
	Logging - ELK (Elastic search Logstash kibana)
	MessagingService - Kafka
	
kafka local:
.\bin\windows\kafka-server-start.bat .\config\server.properties
.\bin\windows\zookeeper-server-start.bat .\config\zookeeper.properties

logstash
.\bin\logstash -f logstash.conf

kibana
bin\kibana.bat

